编者按：马思纯、钟楚曦、黄景瑜主演的影片《荞麦疯长》，原定2月14日情人节上映。
Editor's Note: "Buckwheat Buckwheat Mad" starring Masako, Zhong Chu Xi and Huang Jing Yu was scheduled for February 14.
这是知名电影制片人藤井树自立门户创业后的开业大作，明星云集，拍摄如期完成，公映在即，点映口碑炸裂，原本一切都显得顺风顺水——谁也没想到，天降一只黑天鹅。
This is a well-known film producer Fujiki Fujimori opened his own business, stars gathered, shooting completed on schedule, the public screening of the upcoming explosion, the original everything seems smooth - no one thought that the sky fell a black swan.
口述 |藤井树整理|阿　布我叫藤井树，名字如你所知，来自岩井俊二的电影《情书》。
Rattan & amp; Ab. My name is Fujii. As you know, I came from Junji Ishii's love letter.
你可能听说过“藤井树观影团”，也可能曾经和我们邀请的嘉宾一起看片，对热门影片进行头脑风暴式的讨论。
You may have heard of the Fujimori Filmography Troupe, or you might have seen a film with our invited guests, brainstorming about popular movies.
这个观影团我创办到今年已经有8年多了，每年线下观影超过30场，和同名电影公众号形成了线上线下一定规模的互动。
It's been more than eight years since I started this year, with more than 30 offline views a year, and a certain level of online interaction with the film's public character.
除此之外，我还是个电影制片人和策划人，由我担任总策划的电影《七月与安生》曾经获得金马奖最佳女主角。
In addition to that, I was a film producer and planner, and I won the Golden Horse Award for Best Actress in the overall planning film July and Anson.
2017年我创办了自己的影视公司井树文化，由徐展雄导演，马思纯、钟楚曦、黄景瑜主演的影片《荞麦疯长》是我们公司的开业作。
In 2017, I founded my own film and television company Jingshu culture, directed by Xu Zhixiong, Ma Chu-xi, Huang Jingyu starring in the film "Buckwheat Mad" is the opening of our company.
电影讲述的是上世纪90年代末，小地方的人来到大城市生活的故事，主题之一，我想应该是小人物对命运的不可控吧。
One of the themes of the late 1990s, when people from small places came to live in big cities, was, I think, the uncontrollable fate of the little people.
《荞麦疯长》2.14情人节定档海报这样的不可控，我最近自己也深刻体验了一次。
Buckwheat Mad 2. 14 Valentine's Day posters are so uncontrollable that I have recently experienced them for myself.
电影顺利定档2020情人节后，春节前我们就一直在忙发行和宣传，2019年的12月28日到31日，我们还在江苏常州、山东淄博、河南信阳、广东佛山做了四场提前点映，想听一听来自市场的反应——因为我们不担心一二线城市的票房，就想先探探下沉市场的水深。
From December 28 to 31, 2019, we did four pre-screening screenings in Changzhou, Shandong Zibo, Henan Xinyang and Foshan, Guangdong Province. We wanted to hear from the market because we didn't worry about the box office of a first- or second-tier city, so we wanted to explore the depths of the sinking market.
结果反应相当好，每一场观众都跟着我们又哭又笑，被戏里的人物深深打动。
It turned out to be a pretty good response, with each audience crying and laughing with us, deeply moved by the characters in the play.
山东淄博站点映四场点映做完，我们信心更足了，开始跟演员们碰时间，安排紧凑的各城市路演活动，我还记得那时候黄景瑜已经进了其他组，他跟我说大年三十都要在剧组过了，档期特别满。
In Zibo, Shandong Province, after the four spots were shown, we became more confident and began to meet the actors for a busy road show in various cities. I remember when Huang Jingyu joined other groups.
好不容易把大家的档期都安排好，宣传都做出去了，终极版海报也敲定了，大家都想把年前能做完的事抓紧做完。
It was difficult to arrange all the schedules, publicity has been done, the final version of the poster was finalized, we all want to do what we can do before the year.
1月22日我还在和同事们吃饭聊这些工作，第二天，1月23日，就得知了武汉封城的消息。
On January 22nd, I was having dinner and talking with my colleagues about these jobs. The next day, January 23rd, I learned about the closure of Wuhan.
这一天改变了接下来的所有安排。
That day changed all the arrangements that followed.
很快，7部贺岁档影片一起宣布撤档，我就明白了，我的情人节也没戏了。
Soon, seven New Year's Eve films were pulled together and I knew that my Valentine's Day was over.
疫情会给电影行业带来巨大的打击，而贺岁档撤档只是一个开始，后面会有更长时间的长尾效应——上游投资紧缩，每家公司的日子都不好过，新项目的启动就很难了；正在拍摄中的剧组是最惨的，每停工一天都有巨大的开支，不少项目就因此断了资金链，直接夭折了；原计划二三月开拍的剧组也一定会往后延，延着延着也许就撤资了，不见了；哪怕是已经拍完等待排期上映的电影，比如《荞麦疯长》，至少也要等贺岁档撤下来的多部影片先释放完毕，如此一来，今年的暑期档就一定会显得格外拥挤，竞争异常惨烈。
The film industry will be hit hard by the epidemic, and the New Year's shift is just the beginning, followed by a longer tail effect - upstream investment retrenchment, hard times for every company, new projects are hard to get off the block.
制片人藤井树和三位主演到现在我都觉得《荞麦疯长》还是特别幸运的——2017年，我们还在剧本阶段就获得了上海国际电影节创投单元“最佳创意项目”奖；2018年又获得了吴天明青年电影基金会优秀制片人项目，2019年还参加了戛纳电影节中国馆的中国青年导演系列活动。
Producer Fujimori Fujimori and three other stars were particularly lucky until now - in 2017, we won the Best Creative Project award from the Shanghai International Film Festival's founding unit at the script stage; the Wu Tianming Youth Film Foundation's Excellent Producer Program in 2018; and the Chinese Young Directors Series at the Cannes Film Festival China Pavilion in 2019.
拍摄一切如期非常顺利，2018年8月杀青，2019年通过了内审和技审，拿到龙标和公映许可证，两证齐全，可以进影院安排档期了，最终定档的情人节档期也非常合意——你看，哪怕是一切顺利，一部电影从开始策划到最终定档，中间都要经过漫长的过程，可想而知，在这起码2年的时间里，任何一个阶段遭遇到新冠疫情这只黑天鹅，都会是巨大的打击。
The shooting went smoothly on schedule, in August 2018, it passed IAIG and TAP in 2019, it got the Dragon Band and the Public Viewing License, two certificates were ready to go to the cinema to schedule a schedule, and even if everything went well, it was a long way from the beginning to the end of a movie.
这就好像你跑一个马拉松，不管是出发十米的时候遇到坑，还是离终点十米的时候遇到坑，结果都会摔倒，整个行业里受到牵连的项目是非常多的。
It's like running a marathon, whether you run into a pit ten meters from the finish line or a pit ten meters from the finish line, and you fall and there's a whole industry of projects involved.
马思纯饰云荞钟楚曦饰李麦黄景瑜饰吴风我唯一庆幸的就是我们的电影已经拍完了，不至于停在那里天天烧钱——你知道光是演员留宿酒店的花费都是巨额数字。
/ [^ # 39 ^ # 105 ^ # 105 ^ # 105 ^ # 105 ^ # 105 ^ # 105 ^ # 105 ^ # 105 ^ # 105 ^ # 105] / n. I'm only lucky that our film is finished and doesn't stop there to burn money every day.You know the cost of staying in an actor's hotel alone is huge.
《荞麦疯长》何时才能重新上映？我想首先是等疫情过去，然后开始排队。
When is Buckwheat Mad Buckwheat going to be released again? I think we should wait until the epidemic is over, and then start queuing up.
中间未知数很多，我们唯有等疫情过去之后再做定夺。
There are so many unknowns in the middle that we have to wait until the epidemic is over.
2018年8月《荞麦疯长》杀青眼下我主要考虑的是如何熬过这段没有收入的时间。
Buckwheat Mad in August 2018 The main thing I'm thinking about right now is how to get through this unearned time.
我们是一个民营创业小公司，没有多少余粮，困难还是不小的。
We are a private start-up small company, there is not much surplus grain, the difficulties are not small.
我戏言现在就是“冬眠”，而且是“休克式冬眠”，因为公司的两块业务面临全停——线下的藤井树观影团没法做了，拍好的《荞麦疯长》又只能等待。
I joked that it was "hibernation" and "shock hibernation," because two of the company's businesses were facing a complete shutdown - the underground Fujii Watching Group couldn't do it, and the "Buckwheat Mad" had to wait.
我现在最怕的就是“一眠不醒”，但我也只能选择冬眠，因为动一动都是钱。
What I fear most now is "one cannot wake up," but I can only choose hibernation, because the movement is money.
我相信，疫情过去之后，电影仍然是刚需。
I believe that after the epidemic, the film is still just needed.
但你说会不会出现“报复式观影”，现在还很难说。
But it is too early to say whether there will be "revenge."
因为我觉得这次疫情和非典不同，影响力要大得多，尤其是对人们心理上的影响——几个月的宅家生活会改变很多人的生活方式，哪怕是疫情结束了，初期大家一定也会尽量避免去人多的地方聚集。
Because I think the epidemic is a lot more powerful than SARS, especially the psychological impact - a few months of home life will change the way many people live, even after the epidemic is over, and people will avoid gathering in crowded places at the beginning.
这种心理上的安全感，需要一段时间才能重新找回。
This sense of psychological security will take some time to regain.
最近我的生活就是当全职妈妈，之前因为工作太忙，陪儿子的时间加起来可能都没有现在多，正好多陪陪他。
Recently my life is full-time mother, because of the busy work, may not spend more time with his son, just to accompany him.
导演徐展雄（右）和监制陈正道（左）同时汇报一下《荞麦疯长》的导演，也是我的合伙人徐展雄的近况——他倒是不焦虑，因为他的任务已经完成了，最近正在闭关创作新的剧本——对电影公司来说，现在唯一能干的事情就是在家憋剧本，因为只有剧本是个体劳动，据我所知不少大公司也在囤剧本，希望疫情过去之后，能有好的本子，带领影视市场的复苏。
Director Xu Zhenxiong (right) and producer Chen Zhengdao (left) also report on Buckwheat Mad Length director and partner Xu Jianxiong - he is not worried because his job is done and he is closing the door on new screenplays.
期待疫情过去，影视走出寒冬，荞麦依旧疯长征集令阳春三月，万物复苏。
Looking forward to the epidemic, film and television out of the winter, buckwheat still crazy collection of March, everything recovery.
在抗击疫情的战斗中，我们迎来了春天，《新民周刊》也迎来了新闻线索和故事征集的第二弹。
In the fight against the epidemic, we ushered in the spring, "New People's Weekly" also ushered in the news clues and the second round of story collection.
如今，经历了一个多月休眠的城市正在逐渐苏醒，各行各业都开始有序复工复产。
Now, after more than a month of dormancy of the city is gradually waking up, all walks of life began to orderly resumption of work.
不论您是企业老板、管理者，还是普通员工；又或者，您是老师、家长，还是学生本人……我们希望了解复工复产复学过程中的困难，或暖心故事。
Whether you're a business owner, a manager, or an employee, or whether you're a teacher, parent, or student... we'd like to know about the difficulties of getting back to work, or a warm heart story.
如果你是抗疫一线的医生护士，疫情期间拍下了珍贵的摄影作品，也欢迎联系我们投稿。
If you are a first-line doctor and nurse against the epidemic, you have taken valuable photographs during the epidemic and are welcome to contact us for contributions.
当然，抗击新冠肺炎疫情的相关故事，我们仍然欢迎。
Of course, the story of fighting the outbreak of New Crown Pneumonia is still welcome.
希望广大读者朋友，提供相关线索，说出你的故事，让我们用新闻留存这一切。
I hope that the general reader friends, provide relevant clues, tell your story, let us use the news to retain all this.
